<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">AI Chat Schema Documentation</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        Last Updated: 2025-12-25 22:06 UTC | 
        Version: 0.02 |
        Author: Shanta / Zencoder AI | 
        Status: ✅ COMPLETE - All 6 tables created & automated startup initialized (Phase 1 Done)
    </div>

    <!-- TABLE OF CONTENTS SECTION -->
    <div id="toc" class="row" style="margin: var(--spacing-large) 0; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-color); border-radius: 4px;">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); margin-top: 0;">Quick Navigation</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">Jump to section:</p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--spacing-small);">
                <a href="#overview" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Overview</a>
                <a href="#architecture" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Architecture</a>
                <a href="#table-specs" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Table Specifications</a>
                <a href="#data-flow" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Data Flow</a>
                <a href="#access-control" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Access Control</a>
                <a href="#relationships" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Relationships</a>
                <a href="#performance" style="color: var(--link-color); text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 3px; background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); display: inline-block;">Performance</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- OVERVIEW SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="overview" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">1. Overview</h2>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">The AI Chat system uses a relational database schema to manage conversations, messages, documentation indexing, code searching, and AI model configuration. This schema is built using <strong>DBIx::Class Result classes</strong> (not raw SQL files) for type safety and version control.</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Core Objectives</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Store AI conversations and messages with rich context</li>
                <li>Index documentation for full-text search integration</li>
                <li>Support code searching for developers</li>
                <li>Manage web search results with verification workflow</li>
                <li>Configure AI models per user role</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ARCHITECTURE SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="architecture" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">2. System Architecture</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Database: ENCY (Primary)</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">All AI Chat tables are in the ENCY database, collocated with other application tables.</p>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Tables (6 Total)</h3>
            <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <tr>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Table Name</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Purpose</th>
                    <th style="background-color: var(--table-header-bg); color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Status</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>ai_messages</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Chat messages with conversation context</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">✅ Result class exists</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>documentation_metadata_index</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Full-text search index with metadata</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">✅ Result class exists</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>documentation_role_access</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Role-based access control</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">✅ Result class exists</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>code_search_index</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Code search for developers</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">❌ Result class needed</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>web_search_results</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">Web search results pending verification</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">❌ Result class needed</td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);">
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);"><strong>ai_model_config</strong></td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">AI model configuration by role</td>
                    <td style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); padding: var(--spacing-small); border: 1px solid var(--border-color);">❌ Result class needed</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TABLE SPECIFICATIONS SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="table-specs" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">3. Table Specifications</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">✅ Implementation Status - COMPLETE (Dec 25, 2025)</h3>
            <div style="background-color: #d4edda; padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 2px solid var(--success-color, #28a745); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0; border-left: 4px solid var(--success-color); border-radius: 4px;">
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: 0;"><strong>✅ All AI Chat database tables created and automated startup initialization implemented</strong></p>
                <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                    <li>✅ <strong>ai_messages</strong> - Result class with all fields and relationships</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>documentation_metadata_index</strong> - Full-text search with UNIQUE constraint on file_path</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>documentation_role_access</strong> - Fine-grained access control for documentation sections</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>code_search_index</strong> - Result class created with searchable code and metadata</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>web_search_results</strong> - Result class created with verification workflow support</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>ai_model_config</strong> - Result class created for per-role model configuration</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>DBSchemaManager Integration</strong> - Automated table creation from Result classes on startup</li>
                    <li>✅ <strong>Database Verification</strong> - All tables present in ENCY database with correct columns</li>
                </ul>
                <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0; font-size: var(--font-size-small);"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> Thu Dec 25 2025 22:06 UTC | <strong>Completion Chats:</strong> 12-15 | <strong>Status:</strong> Phase 1 Complete, Ready for Backend Services (Phase 2)</p>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">See Result Class Development Guide</h3>
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">Detailed information about creating Result classes is available in the <a href="/Documentation/Result_Class_Development_Guide" style="color: var(--link-color);">Result Class Development Guide</a>, which provides complete specifications for all table columns, indexes, relationships, and helper methods.</p>
            
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- DATA FLOW SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="data-flow" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">4. Data Flow</h2>
            
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>User Chat Input
    ↓
ai_messages (role='user')
    ↓
AI Processing (using ai_model_config)
    ├─→ Search documentation_metadata_index
    ├─→ Search code_search_index
    └─→ Fetch web_search_results (if verified)
    ↓
ai_messages (role='assistant' with sources_cited)
    ↓
Document sources_cited JSON which references:
    - documentation_metadata_index.file_path
    - code_search_index.file_path
    - web_search_results.id
                </code></pre>
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ACCESS CONTROL SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="access-control" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">5. Access Control</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">documentation_role_access Usage</h3>
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>
# Check if user can access documentation section
my $index = $c->model('DBEncy')->resultset('DocumentationMetadataIndex')
              ->find({file_path => 'admin/settings'});

# Returns true/false based on documentation_role_access rules
my $can_access = $index->can_user_access(['developer', 'user']);
                </code></pre>
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SEARCH FUNCTIONALITY SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="relationships" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">6. Search & Relationships</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Full-Text Search Examples</h3>
            
            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Documentation Search</strong>:</p>
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>SELECT * FROM documentation_metadata_index
WHERE MATCH(searchable_text) AGAINST('user authentication' IN BOOLEAN MODE);
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <p style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);"><strong>Code Search (developer only)</strong>:</p>
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>SELECT * FROM code_search_index
WHERE min_role IN ('developer', 'admin')
  AND MATCH(searchable_code) AGAINST('sub login_check' IN BOOLEAN MODE);
                </code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Relationships Summary</h3>
            <div style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); padding: var(--spacing-medium); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); margin: var(--spacing-small) 0;">
                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>ai_conversations
    ↓
    └─→ has_many ai_messages

ai_messages
    ├─→ belongs_to ai_conversations
    ├─→ belongs_to users (optional)
    └─→ has_many web_search_results (via used_in_ai_message_id)

documentation_metadata_index
    └─→ has_many ai_messages (reverse relation, via sources_cited)

web_search_results
    ├─→ belongs_to users (found_by_user_id)
    ├─→ belongs_to users (verified_by_user_id)
    └─→ belongs_to ai_messages (used_in_ai_message_id)

code_search_index
    └─→ [independent - referenced by ai_messages.sources_cited]

ai_model_config
    └─→ [independent - configuration lookup by (role, agent_type)]

documentation_role_access
    └─→ [independent - access control lookup by (role, doc_section_pattern)]
                </code></pre>
            </div>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PERFORMANCE SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <h2 id="performance" style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font);">7. Performance Considerations</h2>
            
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Indexes Enabled</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>FULLTEXT indexes on <code>searchable_text</code> and <code>searchable_code</code> for fast searches</li>
                <li>UNIQUE constraints on file_path to prevent duplicates</li>
                <li>Regular indexes on frequently filtered columns</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Query Optimization</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>Pre-index documentation files before large-scale use</li>
                <li>Cache ai_model_config lookups (rarely changes)</li>
                <li>Archive old web_search_results to maintain performance</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="text-align: right; margin-top: var(--spacing-small);"><a href="#toc" style="color: var(--link-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">↑ Back to Top</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SEE ALSO SECTION -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-100">
            <div id="see-also" class="success" style="background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-left: 4px solid var(--success-color); padding: var(--spacing-medium); margin: var(--spacing-medium) 0;">
                <h2 style="color: var(--success-color); font-family: var(--header-font); margin-top: 0;">8. See Also</h2>
